    <!-- Core value prop -->
    <div class="content-section-a">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 cvp-boxes">
                    <h1>
                        <img class="img-responsive img-cvp" src="assets/calendar.png" alt="">
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="center">
                        Schedule in advance
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Book ahead and avoid unpredictable surge pricing. Flight delayed? No problem, your driver has your real-time flight info.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 cvp-boxes">
                    <h1>
                        <img class="img-responsive img-cvp" src="assets/expertise.png" alt="">
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="center">
                        Share your expertise
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We all have areas of expertise worth sharing. The secret sauce of Fare Feedback is our proprietary matching algorithm, which pairs you with founders in need of your feedback and perspective.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 cvp-boxes">
                    <h1>
                        <img class="img-responsive img-cvp" src="assets/next-big-thing2.jpg" alt="">
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="center">
                        Discover the future
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Our drivers are all early stage founders. Rather than spending 20 minutes reading emails, have a conversation with our founders, and be the ones telling your friends about the next big thing.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->

    </div>

    <!-- Page Content -->
    <div class="content-section-a">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h1 class="section-heading">Feedback is a Gift</h1>
                    <h3>...that has tangible financial value.</h3>
                    <p class="lead">$40B is spent annually on market research in the US. For scrappy early stage founders, focus groups are both expensive and less effective than a meaningful one-on-one conversation.</p>
                    <!-- <p>Source: http://www.statista.com/topics/1293/market-research/</p> -->
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-6">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="assets/FFB-gift.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->

    </div>
    <!-- /.content-section-a -->

    <div class="content-section-b">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h1 class="section-heading">The sharing economy should involve more sharing.</h1>
                    <p class="lead">...and less sitting in the backseat with your headphones on while checking Facebook. We neither fist bump nor share any of your personal information with our founders, but we do expect you engage in a genuine conversation. Drivers and passengers are not different types of people, and have more in common with each other than you might think.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
