                    <p class="lead">The road ahead is full of unknowns. Only time will tell how <a href="">this crazy idea</a> will evolve. Sign up today, and help us shape the future of the sharing economy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="assets/ipad_pro_roundup.jpg" alt="">
